WEBVTT

00:03:59.567 --> 00:04:00.974
Hamilton's the kind of person

00:04:00.998 --> 00:04:03.227
about whom you would write
a hip-hop musical --

00:04:03.251 --> 00:04:04.278
(Laughter)

00:04:04.302 --> 00:04:05.890
and Madison is the kind of person

00:04:05.914 --> 00:04:08.319
about whom you would not write
a hip-hop musical.

00:04:08.343 --> 00:04:09.363
(Laughter)

00:04:09.387 --> 00:04:11.387
Or indeed, a musical of any kind at all.

00:04:12.372 --> 00:04:13.541
But together,

00:04:13.565 --> 00:04:15.637
they had become a rather unlikely pairing,

00:04:15.661 --> 00:04:17.710
and they had produced
the Federalist Papers,

00:04:17.734 --> 00:04:19.806
which offered a justification

00:04:19.830 --> 00:04:20.995
and, as I mentioned,

00:04:21.019 --> 00:04:23.255
a marketing plan for the Constitution,

00:04:23.279 --> 00:04:27.008
which had been wildly effective
and wildly successful.

00:04:28.529 --> 00:04:30.299
Once the new government was in place,